{"tid":549920,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦白癡一問 關於update BIOS","createTime":"2018-02-04T07:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T10:25:07.000Z","uid":164336,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"79c506d5530785a468c2bb73c3c53e0f8b8d8d11","tid":549920,"uid":164336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T07:40:18.000Z","msg":"小弟想問下 Gigabyte d老母板係咪dl個@BIOS落黎update就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   定係要用個，q-flash？？<br />\n<br />\n事源我部機遇到左個問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.lowyat.net/topic/4248987/all\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.lowyat.net%2Ftopic%2F4248987%2Fall&d=Svi%2FlaPHKyNkjMLWJE565G6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=1f23537f\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.lowyat.net/topic/4248987/all</a><br />\n同呢個post條友基本上一樣<br />\n開機電源著兩秒然後shut down--&gt;1秒左右後再自動著--&gt;正常入第一個畫面--&gt;然後第二個畫面正常係boot from dvd  但依家就花曬 好似個forum條友咁 寫住fix ME fireware data 由1%run到100% --&gt;之後再正常入windows<br />\n依家暫時如果入返windows 都係正常用到<br />\n我research個solution好似係update BIOS<br />\n<br />\n同埋我部機係兩個星期維修過 換左HDD<br />\n佢幫我重新整過d線 好似幾條綁埋一齊咁？ <br />\n跟住我係d台灣論壇見到有人話咩jump？ <br />\n唔知咩可能換底板舊電池事<br />\n其實我真心乜9都唔識 求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/153717_325cf65340b0294276bb5d455ad536c2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F153717_325cf65340b0294276bb5d455ad536c2.png&h=7ed57c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知關唔關windows事 個windows係佢幫我裝埋 而且係試用版  d driver都係<br />\n<br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38d2e60d6b57ff93717deca29911cd0fb2d